## 2. 빠른 시작

### 2.1 새 FreeLang 프로젝트 생성

```bash
$ fpm init my-app kim
Initialized new project 'my-app' with author 'kim'
```

이 명령은 `freelang.toml` 파일을 생성합니다:

```toml
[package]
name = "my-app"
version = "0.1.0"
author = "kim"
description = "A FreeLang project"

[dependencies]
```

### 2.2 의존성 추가

```bash
$ fpm add freelang-json ^1.0.0
Added dependency 'freelang-json' with version range '^1.0.0'
Package: freelang-json
Version: ^1.0.0
Manifest: freelang.toml
```

`freelang.toml`이 자동으로 업데이트됩니다:

```toml
[dependencies]
freelang-json = "^1.0.0"
```

### 2.3 의존성 설치

```bash
$ fpm install
Resolving dependencies...
✓ freelang-json@1.2.3
✓ freelang-http@2.1.0
Total: 2 packages installed
```

### 2.4 패키지 검색

```bash
$ fpm search json
Found 3 package(s) matching 'json'
  freelang-json (1.2.3): JSON parser for FreeLang
  freelang-jsonc (1.1.0): JSONC parser with comments
  freelang-jsond (2.0.0): JSON schema validator
```

